          "name": "Monster Core",
          "page": 209,
          "type": "source"
        }
      ],
      "text": "Some kholos serve as conduits to the divine and are responsible for placating spirits and gods alike. Lamashtu is a favored deity of kholo bonekeepers, as many kholos believe their kind were birthed from the Mother of Monsters. While some kholos embrace the Old Mother completely, others see her as a nightmarish power only to be approached if they're willing to pay the price. Other popular kholo deities include Calistria, Nethys, Mahathallah, or Shelyn.",
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
